summary: This is an automated out-of-office email reply from an FBI agent, indicating they are traveling for work and will respond regarding 'Jeffrey Epstein victims' as soon as possible. It shows FBI activity related to the Epstein case in June 2019.

events.title: FBI Agent Traveling Regarding Epstein Victims
events.description: An FBI agent sends an automatic out-of-office reply indicating they are traveling for work and will respond to correspondence about Jeffrey Epstein victims.

keyFacts: An FBI agent was actively engaged in work related to Jeffrey Epstein victims as of June 25, 2019.
The agent was traveling for work at the time, suggesting field investigation or coordination activities.
The email subject indicates specific FBI correspondence regarding 'Jeffrey Epstein victims' was occurring.
